# Weather Forecast Website 🌦️

This is a simple and professional **Weather Forecast Website** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It fetches real-time weather data from the WeatherAPI and allows users to check the weather of various cities worldwide.

## 🌟 Features
- 🌍 Search for weather updates in multiple cities  
- 📊 Displays temperature, humidity, wind speed, and weather conditions  
- 🎨 Fully responsive design  
- 🚀 Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript  

## 🔧 How to Run
1. Clone the repository:  
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/alvintoor/weather-forecast.git
2. if it did not get weather forecast data go to WeatherAPI and create an account and get APIKEY for that and it will response and work properly then.
